---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Credits" description="The team behind TAOM - Tales From the Age of Men">
  <div class="page-content" style="max-width: 750px;">
    <h1 class="page-title">Credits</h1>

    <div class="credits-intro">
      <p>
        I want to say from the bottom of my heart. <strong>Thank you.</strong> For everything. Very few people understand
        what it takes to build a mod. This mod would be nothing without the past and present team members below.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="credits-section">
      <h2>Helpers/Moderators</h2>
      <p class="section-note">
        Thank you to each and every single helper/moderator. We are currently at almost 2,400 support tickets. That is a
        crazy amount of help provided to the community. It can be quite a thankless job.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Bamba Jay</li>
        <li>ChaseK</li>
        <li>Luiz</li>
        <li>KaiserMax</li>
        <li>Whatman</li>
        <li>Karmaslap</li>
        <li>Arden</li>
        <li>Paszrat</li>
        <li>Bartok</li>
        <li>Elendil</li>
        <li>Ghost</li>
        <li>Theboyys</li>
        <li>Vendetta</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="credits-section">
      <h2>3D Artists</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          KEYforce - <a href="https://www.artstation.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ArtStation</a> - Erkam Kuntay Yi&#287;itcan
        </li>
        <li>Solus</li>
        <li>Nova</li>
